Samsung Electronics to Shift Solar Business to SDI, Economic Daily Reports

-- B y   S h i n h y e   K a n g
-- 
2011-05-27T02:05:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-27/samsung-electronics-to-shift-solar-business-to-sdi-economic-daily-reports.html
Samsung Electronics Co. will transfer
its solar-cell business to Samsung SDI Co., the Korea Economic
Daily reported, without saying where it got the information.
Samsung Electronics will hand over personnel and facilities to
SDI, according to the Korean-language newspaper.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Shinhye Kang at 
 skang24@bloomberg.net  